        "It’s been a year since I left [Paul]. Helpie and I have been very wary of [him] ever since, and It’s been weird going to class together, but still, I wouldn’t want it any other way. "
      ],
      [
        "I’ve actually focused on my work and did a bunch of projects that I’ve felt proud about, that even got me some friends! I’ve noticed that [Paul] sometimes looks at me with resentment, but whatever. "
      ],
      [
        "And Helpie and I had gotten even closer ever since. We’ve grown to be like family, but most importantly, I know I can trust in Them more than anybot in the world."
      ],
      [
        "[tn]! It’s time to go to the cinema, you comin’ right? "
      ],
      [
        "Yeah! sorry, my mind drifted away."
      ],
      [
        "I’ve never felt happier… with myself and with my life… welp, gotta go!"
